---
title: Chicken, Mushroom and Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto Rigatoni with Parmesan Cheese
description: A familiar and delicious pasta dish full of flavor and heartiness. Inspired by "Hunter" stews, this recipe brings together tender pieces of chicken,  earthy mushrooms and a lightly tomato sauce for ultimate comfort and tasty satisfaction.
